social_posts.post_text: Meet Dusty: Dusty is a Wisconsin native and former firefighter. He moved to New York City to pursue his acting passions and used his skill in front of the camera to model for many brands including Ralph Lauren, Calvin Klein, and Frame. He is currently the face of the Stetson Spirit fragrance commercial and campaign. Dusty has been shot by photographers such as Bruce Weber, Mario Testino, and Mariano Vivanco. He recently made his acting debut as Jasper Collins in Public School Pictures’ 13TH STEPPING. #DUSTYLACHOWICZ #BACKTOSCHOOL #PUBLICSCHOOLPICTURES

Curator, Giuliana Vidarte, suggested I explore Amazonian mythologies.
The 'Bufeo Colorado' was the first that captured my mind and imagination.
Dusty Lachowicz is the Bufeo Colorado.
//
Curadora, Giuliana Vidarte, me sugirió explorar las mitologías amazónicas.
El 'Bufeo Colorado' fue el primero que capturó mi mente y mi imaginación.
Dusty Lachowicz es el Bufeo Colorado.

When the European settlers
come to the Amazonian jungle, local men noticed their newborn children's skin looked conspicuously lighter than themselves or their partners.  They would consult their female counterparts and ask how this happened. Wives and companions would blame this on the Bufeo Colorado.
According to this tale, the transformation of this pink, shape-shifting river dolphin happens on nights of the full moon. The dolphin morphs into a tall, handsome, light-skinned man who steps ashore and sets out to seduce the wives and daughters of the Amazonian villages. 🇵🇪🇵🇪🇵🇪
//
Cuando los colonos europeos
vinieron la selva amazónica, los hombres locales notaron que la piel de sus hijos recién nacidos parecía notoriamente más clara que la de ellos o la de sus parejas.  Consultaban a sus homólogas femeninas y les preguntaban cómo sucedió esto.  Esposas y compañeras culparían de esto al Bufeo Colorado.
Según este cuento, la transformación de este delfín rosado de río que cambia de forma ocurre en las noches de luna llena. El delfín se transforma en un hombre alto, guapo y de piel clara que desembarca y se propone seducir a las esposas e hijas de los pueblos amazónicos. 🇵🇪🇵🇪🇵🇪
